    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Beginning at 9th level, you can roll one additional weapon damage die when determining the extra damage for a critical hit with a melee attack. This increases to two additional dice at 13th level and three additional dice at 17th level.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>You have two automation options:</em></p>\n<ol>\n<li><em>In your character's Special Traits, manually set Melee Weapon Critical Damage Dice to the number of dice granted by this feature.</em></li>\n<li><em>Set your melee weapon's Extra Critical Hit Damage to (@scale.barbarian.brutal-critical)d12 â€” change the damage die to match your weapon's damage dice.</em></li>\n</ol>\n</section>",
